deck: The second issue of Killing Blood and drugs
description:
Dana in disguise... tortured for the sins of the one she's impersonating! A vice racketeer doing the bidding of the KGB! Things are not always how they seem... Especially when the Diabolical Super-criminal Killing is involved, as in this tale of sex, drugs, espionage and death!

Drug Bomb: Gangsters steal an experimental "super-heroin" which packs a bigger punch than anyone expected. Knowing its true secret, Killing and Dana plot to steal the plunder for their own nefarious designs in this tale of addiction, forbidden lust, greed, betrayal and death!
name: Sangue E Droga

deck: The King of Crime!
description:
Death Diamonds: A cache of hot sparklers triggers a bloodbath when the tenacious King of Crime plots to purloin the gems from a cadre of gangsters, hoodlums and scheming hellions! And how are the Monte Carlo police able to track the every move of the Monster with 1000 Masks? A movie length photo novel with primal terror, murder, sex, and vicious duplicity!!

Notes

It is theorized that while this is the 4th issue in the series, it was actually the 1st story. The title, The king of Crime, is a description/introduction of Killing. Despite appearing on the cover, Killing does not have his belt of death on in any of the interior photos (the belt is in all of the other issues). Also, this is the only original issue that does not feature Dana.

At the end of the issue there is an Artcile introducing Italian readers to actress Raquel Welch.
name: Il Re del Delitto

deck: One too many blondes
description: Violence visits a voyeur: In a rare moment of relaxation, Killing lets down his guard and his most protected secret is exposed! Blackmailed by a scheming pin-up model, Killing engages in a deadly plot that involves dolls, drugs and death!
name: Una Bionda di troppo

deck: Night of terror
description: Ras, France's king of the underworld, decides to challenge Killing in a game of death.
name: Notte di terrore

deck: Check the underworld.
description: Strip & Kill: A top secret poison gas formula is the target of the King of Crime. But a mob boss and spies are also after the plans and the F.B.I. is hot on all their trails! Can Killing succeed as he has to wade through rivers of blood, corpses and traitorous vixens?
name: Scacco alla malavita

description: Monte Carlo, wonderful gem on the sea where you give billions conference bored, every part of the world, but where often under the patina of luxury and carefree, hide terrible secrets, and where the Intercontinental underworld loves camouflage to escape the clutches of the ruthless law
name: Bambole e dollari
